    • addTrail

      public void addTrail​(model.Trail trail)
      This method adds a trail to the trail store. It will add two trails that are the same. It adds it too each data structure which all contain a LinkedList at a key.
      Parameters:
      Trail - trail

    • searchByName

      public java.util.List<model.Trail> searchByName​(java.lang.String searchPhrase)
      This method searches through the LinkedList that contains all the names of trails to return any trail with the searchPhrase in it. For example if you searched tree, both a trail named tree woods and tree place would be returned.
      Parameters:
      searchPhrase -
      Returns:
      List
